snippet.title: The Nameless City itch.io release trailer
snippet.description:
The Nameless City is a first person adventure/walking simulator inspired by Lovecraft's short novel of the same name. It has lo-fi 3D graphics inspired by the PSX era​.
You can play the demo and buy the full game on itch.io: paradnight-studio.itch.io/the-nameless-city
#lovecraft #psx #horror #indiegame
